If you use GAZR for your academic work, please cite this paper:

Lemaignan et al. "From Real-time Attention Assessment to “With-me-ness” in Human-Robot Interaction". HRI 2016.

For LaTeX users, you can use this BibTeX entry:

@inproceedings{lemaignan2016realtime,
  author = {Lemaignan, S. and 
            Garcia, F. and 
            Jacq, A. and 
            Dillenbourg, P.},
  title = {From Real-time Attention Assessment to “With-me-ness” in Human-Robot Interaction},
  booktitle = {Proceedings of the 2016 ACM/IEEE Human-Robot Interaction Conference},
  year = {2016},
  url = {http://github.com/severin-lemaignan/gazr}
}
